  "page": "Aron (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Aron_Santagar\" title=\"Aron Santagar\">Aron Santagar</a></b> is the master-at-arms at the Red Keep.\n</p><p>Other characters named <b>Aron</b> or its variants include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Arron\" title=\"Arron\">Arron</a>, a Night's Watch recruit</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arron_Qorgyle\" title=\"Arron Qorgyle\">Arron Qorgyle</a>, a Dornish knight</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Barron_Durrandon\" title=\"Barron Durrandon\">Barron Durrandon</a>, a Storm King</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Camarron_of_the_Count\" title=\"Camarron of the Count\">Camarron of the Count</a>, a pit fighter in Meereen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garon_Baratheon\" title=\"Garon Baratheon\">Garon Baratheon</a>, a knight from the Stormlands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harron_Harlaw\" title=\"Harron Harlaw\">Harron Harlaw</a>, a High King of the Iron Islands</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maron_Botley\" title=\"Maron Botley\">Maron Botley</a>, an ironborn raider</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Maron Greyjoy\">Maron Greyjoy</a>, a son of Lord Balon Greyjoy</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maron_Martell\" title=\"Maron Martell\">Maron Martell</a>, a ruling Prince of Dorne</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maron_Volmark\" title=\"Maron Volmark\">Maron Volmark</a>, a Lord of Volmark</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260407042300\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!